dct_title_s: Map of Southern Manchuria and Northern Korea
dct_description_sm: Includes legend, "Glossary for place names," "Approximate distances by rail in miles" (table).
Inset map showing railroad from St. Petersburg to east coast of Chinese Empire.
Shows waterways, railroads (including under construction), main and minor roads, Korea-Manchuria boundary.
